              <text value="This program was written to be a simple educational projects that shows how to use some resources of Graphical User Interface (Swing) from Java language and some software engineering techniques. The aim of the program is performing the conversion between two measure units.&#10;&#10;All the action is places in the background panel of the main screen. The user interacts with this screen most of the times.&#10;&#10;The menu options are very straight:&#10;- At Help menu you will open this screen;&#10;- At the Credits menu, you will see the names and identifiers of the group responsible by this project.&#10;&#10;To use the program:&#10;- Fill the field &quot;Convert from&quot; with a number;&#10;- Choose in which unit system this number is, at the first combo;&#10;- Choose the result unit at the second combo;&#10;- The result value will appeat at the &quot;to&quot; field!" noi18n="true"/>
